creator: Branded Brothers
descriptionHtml:
Bubble pop everything with the most funny and adorable Bubble Wizard in history in this classic casual game: bubble shooter. Match 3 or more bubbles by colors and clear levels along a magical bubble pop adventure.

Be calm to aim and shoot in order to match bubbles and get magic potions, free some magical stars and make every bubble pop!. Simple and easy to learn, great for all ages.

Some Features:
- Great graphics and sound design to make a calm and relaxing player experience.
- Lots of challenging bubbling puzzles adventures to complete!
- Intuitive, easy and guaranty fun play.
- 3 magical Boosters to help you along the way and reach high scores.
- A cute and funny Wizard!.

How to Play a match 3 bubble game?

1. Tap and aim where you want to shoot a bubble.
2. Match 3 or more bubbles to make them pop.
3. Complete the goal for each level (up to 4 different goals).
4. Get the three stars on each level and become a Bubble wizard master!

We hope you enjoy playing Bubble Wizard!
